We have performed a re-annotation of the [Multiview Extended Video with Activities (MEVA)](https://registry.opendata.aws/mevadata/) dataset by:

1. Decomposing the videos into individual frames;
2. Applying computer vision algorithms for automated annotation;
3. Implementing manual verification of the annotations;
4. Reconstructing the frames back into complete video sequences;

The resulting annotated dataset is intended for AI model training and research in multi-view human activity scenarios.
